13) Write a program to find the percentage of uppercase letters, lowercase letters, digits and special characters in a given string?
14) Write a program to prove that strings are immutable ?
15) How do you find longest substring without repeating characters in the given string?
16) How do you swap two string variables without using third or temp variable ?
17) Write a program to find all permutations of a string?
